{"tid":2442603,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"人大《完善選舉制度決定》對香港人未嘗不是一件好事。","createTime":"2021-03-11T12:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T06:21:46.000Z","uid":219007,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f32ea0551ee4e59151914e5e3cebd69d195d0ea9","tid":2442603,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"對方正式撕下畫皮，名副其實玩撚完<br />\n<br />\n香港人之間終於唔需要再扮撚晒野，為呢個制度扮乜扮物，又政改又幾多部曲，民主黨又點諗，公民黨又點諗，本土派又點諗.....<br />\n<br />\n過去真心發夢嘅人亦都會夢醒，而仲未瞓醒嘅只會淪為笑柄，最終無人問津。<br />\n<br />\n由呢一刻開始，香港人終於徹徹底底面對現實。即時走嘅走，搵多幾個錢先走既留多幾年，決定唔走嘅就要喺度搵出路，投共又好乜都好，各有選擇，人各有志。<br />\n<br />\n30年夢回，話早唔早，話遲唔遲，總好過未醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463dd8f2830b3a4580777fdff7f6528668a8b82e","tid":2442603,"uid":76591,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"好事<br />\n傳統建制派會畀新香港人取代<br />\n三萬香港汪汪會畀中國小粉紅取代<br />\n皆大歡喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb96bc27fb26e953a36e0db9d6b0437c2671e61","tid":2442603,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:44:38.000Z","msg":"共業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254a6d11f4218610e014a2db372e2b679634ddc3","tid":2442603,"uid":114193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"做順民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為連下sir 忠實信徒<br />\n堅決支持連下sir 信念：<br />\n反黑暴，保政權，黃屍港毒一齊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我copy連下sir 每日嘅大作你哋睇<br />\n震懾下你班連登黑暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大DQ學生會一事足以證明只能放棄香港，留底只能夠選擇表忠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423210</a><br />\n<br />\n「安心出行」根本就冇得避，留底既香港人只會能夠接受～<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2401117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2401117</a><br />\n<br />\n依家講到明連選舉都唔俾你玩，請問啲留港抗爭撚點睇？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2417881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2417881</a><br />\n<br />\n［改變心態］香港變成點唔重要，最緊要自己活得開心就足夠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2368342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2368342</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2329311/page/1</a><br />\n肥佬黎俾人告國安法，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2323506/page/1</a><br />\n中大畢業遊行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2315353/page/1</a><br />\n拜登贏咗，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1</a><br />\n就黎國安法實行，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1</a><br />\n612一周年，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1</a><br />\n有武肺，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1</a><br />\nPoly 打完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768364/page/1</a><br />\n要選區議會，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1681018/page/1</a><br />\n機場壓力測試完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1548844/page/1</a><br />\n8月大罷工完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417635/page/1</a><br />\n728元朗遊行完，散水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1383029/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"424955ef4d580f8500dad493e3a387fae5833327","tid":2442603,"uid":301538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:55:45.000Z","msg":"講個笑話比大家聽<br />\n五十年不變"},{"pid":"451019815dea754cdb3edaff3ee41d5fec2ef7a3","tid":2442603,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f32ea0551ee4e59151914e5e3cebd69d195d0ea9","tid":2442603,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"對方正式撕下畫皮，名副其實玩撚完<br />\n<br />\n香港人之間終於唔需要再扮撚晒野，為呢個制度扮乜扮物，又政改又幾多部曲，民主黨又點諗，公民黨又點諗，本土派又點諗.....<br />\n<br />\n過去真心發夢嘅人亦都會夢醒，而仲未瞓醒嘅只會淪為笑柄，最終無人問津。<br />\n<br />\n由呢一刻開始，香港人終於徹徹底底面對現實。即時走嘅走，搵多幾個錢先走既留多幾年，決定唔走嘅就要喺度搵出路，投共又好乜都好，各有選擇，人各有志。<br />\n<br />\n30年夢回，話早唔早，話遲唔遲，總好過未醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"面具仲存在緊。<br />\n<br />\n中共會話：<br />\n1）只係要黎對付反中亂港的攬炒暴政派<br />\n2）因為黑暴所以暫時減少直接民主議席<br />\n3）選委會多左人，代表性更高<br />\n4）立法會多左人，更具代表性"},{"pid":"ecd23fee28533703865028f06a1124009af1f09a","tid":2442603,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:26:26.000Z","msg":"黎緊禮義廉_ 同佢地旗下D &quot;義工組織&quot; 又會搞D簽名站, 話叫人支持乜乜完善選舉制..........<br />\n仲要响一般人返工時間搞.....<br />\n<br />\nTarget 就係班C9 同老人家~!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家門不幸..